"     Reproduced with permission from: Cho ME, Kopp JB. Fabry disease in the era of enzyme replacement therapy: a renal perspective. Pediatr Nephrol 2004; 19:583. Copyright &copy; 2004 Springer Science and Business Media.",
"    </div>",
